1
00:00:04,904 --> 00:00:05,904
Hei Yan,

2
00:00:07,249 --> 00:00:08,817
you're not actually
falling for him, are you?

3
00:00:08,842 --> 00:00:09,842
I'm not.

4
00:00:10,443 --> 00:00:11,678
You'd better not be.

5
00:00:12,379 --> 00:00:13,939
Otherwise, I'll put out a press release

6
00:00:14,381 --> 00:00:15,748
saying he seduced you

7
00:00:15,749 --> 00:00:16,749
just to get some clout.

8
00:00:17,650 --> 00:00:18,852
Don't go twisting the facts.

9
00:00:19,386 --> 00:00:21,021
I have my own way of doing things.

10
00:00:21,921 --> 00:00:23,223
I'm going to use this hype

11
00:00:23,690 --> 00:00:25,325
to crush him and boost your following.

12
00:00:28,928 --> 00:00:29,928
Bingchen,

13
00:00:29,996 --> 00:00:31,297
I know I'm your artist,

14
00:00:31,831 --> 00:00:33,111
but I'd appreciate some respect.

15
00:00:34,734 --> 00:00:36,494
We'll talk about respect
when you're a star.

16
00:00:37,103 --> 00:00:38,271
You have to be ruthless.

17
00:00:39,672 --> 00:00:40,672
Isn't the whole point of these stunts

18
00:00:40,673 --> 00:00:41,608
to make the company money?

19
00:00:41,609 --> 00:00:42,674
Isn't that what you're here for?

20
00:00:42,675 --> 00:00:44,077
Why do you have to play so dirty?

21
00:00:44,444 --> 00:00:45,145
Don't you know me by now?

22
00:00:45,146 --> 00:00:46,879
I'll do whatever it takes to get results.

23
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:47,880
You...

24
00:00:53,753 --> 00:00:55,587
Sharp. Very sharp.

25
00:00:55,588 --> 00:00:56,423
You've had too much to drink.

26
00:00:56,424 --> 00:00:58,290
Anyone Bingchen takes under his wing

27
00:00:58,291 --> 00:00:59,559
is bound to be impressive.

28
00:01:00,226 --> 00:01:01,060
You know it.

29
00:01:01,061 --> 00:01:02,395
Fame and fortune for everyone.

30
00:01:02,929 --> 00:01:04,831
If you're happy, I'm happy.

31
00:01:05,265 --> 00:01:06,232
Oh, come on, Mike.

32
00:01:06,233 --> 00:01:08,133
You're the one who saw

33
00:01:08,134 --> 00:01:09,602
Hei Yan's potential from the start.

34
00:01:10,070 --> 00:01:12,104
You should really thank Hei Yan.

35
00:01:12,105 --> 00:01:14,674
He's the one who convinced
me with all that data.

36
00:01:15,975 --> 00:01:17,410
Exactly, Mike.

37
00:01:17,677 --> 00:01:19,078
That's how a professional artist

38
00:01:19,079 --> 00:01:20,145
is supposed to act.

39
00:01:20,146 --> 00:01:21,447
Poor Shasha

40
00:01:21,448 --> 00:01:23,450
was devastated by all of this.

41
00:01:23,683 --> 00:01:24,250
You know,

42
00:01:24,251 --> 00:01:26,119
a simple dinner won't make up for it.

43
00:01:27,387 --> 00:01:28,188
Fine...

44
00:01:28,189 --> 00:01:30,349
I'll get her an endorsement
deal to make it up to her.

45
00:01:30,790 --> 00:01:31,834
Come on, let's have another round.

46
00:01:31,858 --> 00:01:32,858
Sounds good.

47
00:01:42,869 --> 00:01:44,369
All that effort...

48
00:01:44,370 --> 00:01:45,672
just to put on a show.
